			IMPORTANT
--------------------------------------------------------

the new clients always attach aside the master
hence the slave no1 as i like to understand it.

--------------------------------------------------------
			INSTALLATION
--------------------------------------------------------

After cloning this repo, run as root:
	make clean install

this should install dwm, then add it to your 
.xinitrc to run with startx

--------------------------------------------------------
			STATUS BAR
--------------------------------------------------------
you can update the status info of your bar by
adding the following to your .xinitrc:

while xsetroot -name "`date` `uptime | sed 's/.*,//'`"
do
sleep 1
done &

howeveer using dwmblocks is highly recommended
